							></path></svg
						>
					</a>
					<a
						href='https://www.instagram.com/igeco_providingthefuture/?igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D'
						target='_blank'
					>
						<svg
							class='fill-white h-8'
							role='img'
							viewBox='0 0 24 24'
							xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
